description:
Chobani Blueberry Greek Yogurt Plump blueberries are dropped into our low fat Greek Yogurt to create the perfect snack

With over 13 grams of protein in every pot its perfect on its own as an afternoon snack or a flavour filled addition to your morning muesli

At Chobani we believe yogurt should be simple just milk and cultures which we strain using a centuries old authentic process to make it deliciously thick It takes 3 cups of milk to make 1 cup of Chobani Yogurt which is why its so creamy and packed with protein All Chobani fruit pots contain this thick and creamy yogurt layered on a foundation of real fruit sure to delight your taste buds

No preservatives artificial colours or flavours

High in natural protein
name: Chobani Blueberry Greek Yogurt Yoghurt 170g
